{"data":[{"date":"10:27 09/07","title":"Fernandinho b\u1ecb d\u1ecda gi\u1ebft v\u00ec b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi trong tr\u1eadn Brazil thua B\u1ec9","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/fernandinho-bi-doa-giet-vi-ban-phan-luoi-trong-tran-brazil-thua-bi.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4078","checkdouble":"190755"},{"date":"10:38 09/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc c\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00ec h\u1ecdc sinh h\u1ecdc th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/9/truong-hoc-cam-bong-da-vi-hoc-sinh-hoc-thoi-an-va-cua-neymar.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2> M\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i Anh \u0111\u00e3 ban b\u1ed1 l\u1ec7nh c\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua v\u00ec t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng h\u1ecdc sinh c\u1ed1 b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb xem World Cup qua truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc c\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00ec h\u1ecdc sinh b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc c\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00ec h\u1ecdc sinh b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/1_4.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc Home Farm s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sportbible, tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc Home Farm t\u1ea1i Colchester, Anh \u0111\u00e3 ban b\u1ed1 l\u1ec7nh c\u1ea5m m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 trong c\u00e1c gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao b\u1edfi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng h\u1ecdc sinh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n tranh c\u00e3i, x\u00f4 x\u00e1t nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t \u00fd th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng &quot;tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1&quot; c\u1ee7a Neymar: &quot;\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u em h\u1ecdc sinh c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexico. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i, t\u1eeb 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 11 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft em n\u00e0o c\u0169ng l\u00e0m theo c\u1eadu ta&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch c\u00e1c em v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2n ch\u00ednh&quot;, ban gi\u00e1m hi\u1ec7u nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ee5 huynh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u1ee9ng nh\u01b0ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u00fd ki\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. H\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng con em c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00f2a chung v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dau an tai World Cup cua Neymar la 2 ban thang cung vo so pha an va.\" title=\"D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u1ee7a Neymar l\u00e0 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 pha \u0103n v\u1ea1.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/3_1.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u1ee7a Neymar l\u00e0 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 pha \u0103n v\u1ea1.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i \u0111ang lan truy\u1ec1n \u0111o\u1ea1n video c\u00e1c em h\u1ecdc sinh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f4 vang &quot;Neymar&quot;, c\u00e1c em s\u1ebd ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c n\u1eb1m ra s\u00e2n la h\u00e9t v\u1edbi v\u1ebb \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ronaldo &quot;b\u00e9o&quot; kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i: &quot;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y d\u00e0nh cho Neymar. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 t\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng b\u1ea1o l\u1ef1c&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3u c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1eadp. Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a. Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n l\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y nh\u1eefng trang tin c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd&quot;, Sky Sports d\u1eabn l\u1eddi Ronaldo &quot;b\u00e9o&quot;.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4077","checkdouble":"190756"},{"date":"09:27 09/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed5i gi\u1edd thi \u0111\u1ea5u, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng U19 \u0110N\u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/doi-gio-thi-dau-u19-viet-nam-con-co-hoi-vuot-qua-vong-bang-u19-dna.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1edd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p U19 Singapore nh\u1eb1m mang t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><h2>L\u00f9i gi\u1edd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Singapore</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 Indonesia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong manh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eadm Singapore c\u00f2n Indonesia th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp Th\u00e1i Lan th\u00ec U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 may v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u00f9i gi\u1edd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Singapore h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u00f9i gi\u1edd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Singapore h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/U19-Viet-Nam-duoc-yeu-cau-tap-trung-toi-da-tran-gap-Singapore-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BTC gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00f9i gi\u1edd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Singapore</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, BTC gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh gi\u1edd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p U19 Singapore. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 15h30 nh\u01b0 ban \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00ec tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn Indonesia- Th\u00e1i Lan l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i nay 9/7.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee1 b\u1ecb thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 4 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 r\u1ea5t cao ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm khi ch\u00fang ta x\u1ebfp sau U19 Th\u00e1i Lan (10 \u0111i\u1ec3m) v\u00e0 U19 Indonesia (12 \u0111i\u1ec3m).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i, Indonesia s\u1ebd tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed l\u1eeda tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i nguy cho U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH U19 DNA 2018\" title=\"BXH U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Untitled.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u19-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-168-190686.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/u19-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u19-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-168-190686.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nV\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 Indonesia trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i qua 7/7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-01-u19-indonesia-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190633.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-01-u19-indonesia-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-01-u19-indonesia-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190633.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-1 U19 Indonesia (Gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1nh c\u1eeda v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1eb9p \u0111i tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y sau khi ch\u00fang ta thua U19 Indonesia, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n v\u00e0o...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4076","checkdouble":"190749"},{"date":"09:46 09/07","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/8/cong-phuong-len-tieng-sau-tinh-huong-mat-kiem-che-voi-thu-mon-tuan-manh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh b\u00ean ph\u00eda Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</h2><h2>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee9a thay \u0111\u1ed5i sau pha&nbsp;n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng v\u1edbi Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Pleiku \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 4-2, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0nh vi n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn l\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi qua ti\u1ebfng l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, bu\u1ed9c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"cong phuong\" title=\"c\u00f4ng ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/cong-phuong-len-tieng-sau-tinh-huong-mat-kiem-che-voi-thu-mon-tuan-manh.png\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00e2u gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. \u1ea2nh: Sport5.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 \u00fd g\u00e2y h\u1ea5n sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. Th\u00f4ng qua trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Anh n\u00f3i: &quot;H\u00f4m nay th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y kh\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n nh\u01b0ng mong l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00f2ng tin v\u00e0 hi v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00ecnh bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u00e0 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng m\u00ecnh lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. H\u00f4m nay, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e3y hi\u1ec3u cho m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea7n t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 &ldquo;bu\u1ed3n&rdquo; c\u00f2n bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec c\u00e1i g\u00ec ch\u1eafc m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u00f9ng nhau c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HAGL. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai. Tuy nhi\u00ean Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League sau vong 18\" title=\"BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/BXH-V-League-sau-vong-18.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm song CLB HAGL cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. V\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4075","checkdouble":"190750"},{"date":"09:02 09/07","title":"Sao s\u00e1ng World Cup x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/torreira-sap-toi-arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lucas Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf. Ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y v\u1edbi b\u00e1o ch\u00ed.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Torreira t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u00e0 World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u0103m 2013, Lucas Torreira r\u1eddi qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Uruguay \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Italia \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Pescara. Ch\u1ec9 sau v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Serie B, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Sampdoria v\u00e0 h\u1ecd chi 1,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 anh. Sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 Torreira ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i cho Pescara d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u00f9a 2015/16, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng tri\u1ec7u h\u1ed3i anh v\u1ec1 v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 2 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua, Torreira \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i 35 tr\u1eadn tr\u1edf l\u00ean t\u1ea1i Serie A cho Sampdoria. \u1ede m\u00f9a 2017/18, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ph\u00e1t ti\u1ebft m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng (ch\u1ec9 cao 1m68) song Torreira c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Torreira-sap-toi-Arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Torreira ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i Sampdoria</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Torreira n\u1eb1m \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nhanh nh\u01b0 c\u1eaft. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Uruguay c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0 ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t hay s\u00fat xa\u2026 T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Serie A hay m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau m\u00f9a 2017/18, Arsenal v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 Torreira \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1o li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Sampdoria \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua anh. Sau c\u00f9ng, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 26,4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Torreira\" title=\"tien ve Torreira\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/torreira-sap-toi-arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, sau khi Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0111i k\u00e8m Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf. Anh c\u0169ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f9ng ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Uruguay c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d, Torreira n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Telenoche. \u201cNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed n\u00f3.\u201d <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi Arsenal, Torreira s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng Stephan Lichtsteiner, Bernd Leno v\u00e0 Sokratis Papastathopoulos \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV m\u1edbi Unai Emery thay Arsene Wenger.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-arsenal-van-chua-the-cong-bo-thuong-vu-torreira-172-190606.html\">V\u00ec sao Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Torreira?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-arsenal-chi-27-trieu-bang-mua-cristian-pavon-172-190516.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal chi 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Cristian Pavon</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/arsenal-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-vu-sao-khung-argentina-421-190433.html\">Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Argentina</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-barca-172-190353.html\">Arsenal b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4074","checkdouble":"190746"},{"date":"10:02 09/07","title":"Arsenal chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/arsenal-chuan-bi-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-than-dong-guendouzi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0a tin, Arsenal \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Matteo Guendouzi.</h2><h2>Arsenal s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Matteo Guendouzi\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin \u0111\u1ed3n Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Guendouzi trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin \u0111\u1ed3n Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Guendouzi trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/arsenal-chuan-bi-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-than-dong-guendouzi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Guendouzi, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal</span> \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Lorient \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Matteo Guendouzi h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i. Anh l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb PSG nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Lorient n\u0103m 2014.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd RMC Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t v\u00e0 Guendouzi s\u1ebd bay t\u1edbi London trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates. Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y khi Guendouzi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCLB Lorient c\u1ee7a Guendouzi \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng kh\u1ecfi Ligue 1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tranh su\u1ea5t th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Guendouzi c\u00f3 21 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u01a1i ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd do Guendouzi r\u1eddi Lorient \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Guendouzi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ee1 quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Lorient. Anh b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Do v\u1eady, ra \u0111i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Guendouzi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u t\u1ea1i Ph\u1ea7n Lan s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 khi Torreira c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi London sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay \u1edf World Cup 2018. Theo nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Torreira, anh s\u1ebd ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m London Colney trong h\u00f4m nay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/torreira-sap-toi-arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te-172-190746.html\">Sao s\u00e1ng World Cup x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-arsenal-van-chua-the-cong-bo-thuong-vu-torreira-172-190606.html\">V\u00ec sao Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Torreira?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4073","checkdouble":"190748"},{"date":"10:51 09/07","title":"Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 c\u00f9ng Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/12/elneny-hao-huc-truoc-mua-giai-201819-cung-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mohamed Elneny t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 khi Arsenal b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd.</h2><h2>Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo. Anh kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn derby London v\u1edbi West Ham h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Elneny \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc Phi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Pharaoh c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m do \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 c\u00f9ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 c\u00f9ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/elneny-hao-huc-truoc-mua-giai-201819-cung-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quay l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Emirates, Elneny \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. HLV Unai Emery s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m tr\u00e1ch vi\u1ec7c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y sau khi HLV Wenger ra \u0111i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Elneny v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau khi tham d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, anh s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00e8 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p Boreham Wood v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 14/7 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00e2n binh</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng n\u0103ng n\u1ed5. HLV Unai Emery b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ecdng y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno, trung\u00a0 v\u1ec7 Sokratis, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Lichtsteiner l\u00e0 3 t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Lucas Torreira c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u0169ng m\u1edbi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn London ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chuan-bi-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-than-dong-guendouzi-172-190748.html\">Arsenal chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-arsenal-van-chua-the-cong-bo-thuong-vu-torreira-172-190606.html\">V\u00ec sao Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Torreira?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4072","checkdouble":"190754"},{"date":"08:50 09/07","title":"Evra khuy\u00ean Ronaldo t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU, gia nh\u1eadp Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/9/evra-khuyen-ronaldo-tu-choi-mu-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Patrice Evra tin r\u1eb1ng Juventus l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</h2><h2>Ronaldo s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Real Madrid h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ee1 quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi HLV Florentino Perez. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia l\u00e0 Juventus \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadt l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a CR7 v\u1ec1 Turin v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-dung-luong-sieu-khung-du-ronaldo-tro-lai-old-trafford-172-183045.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man United \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford</span>. <br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Evra khuy\u00ean Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Evra khuy\u00ean Ronaldo t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU, gia nh\u1eadp Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Evra khuy\u00ean Ronaldo t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU, gia nh\u1eadp Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/evra-khuyen-ronaldo-tu-choi-mu-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Evra khuy\u00ean Ronaldo t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU, gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng Evra, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i cho c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cho r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n Ronaldo n\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Italia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cM\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u h\u1ecfi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn Juventus hay Man United. T\u00f4i th\u00ec v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2050, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1eady th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Juventus. B\u1edfi v\u00ec sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Man United, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ea1y. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0103n ch\u00e1o \u0111\u00e1 b\u00e1t n\u00ean Juve s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n \u1edf trong tr\u00e1i tim t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Ronaldo r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn. C\u1eadu bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia y\u00eau c\u1eadu th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 hy sinh n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ebfn Juve. C\u1eadu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y m\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juve, Ronaldo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup ti\u1ebfp theo ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t linh v\u1eadt c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ronaldo:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/modric-khong-tin-ronaldo-se-roi-real-180-190697.html\">Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo-180-190689.html\">C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real v\u1ec1 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4071","checkdouble":"190744"},{"date":"08:33 09/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Paulinho \u0111i th\u1eadt xa \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1... Trung Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/12/21/chinh-thuc-tien-ve-paulinho-roi-barca-chi-sau-11-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Barcelona \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paulinho tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u H\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ea1i ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, ch\u1ec9 11 th\u00e1ng sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i.\r\n</h2><h2>Paulinho ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Barca<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2017, G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Paulinho \u2013 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c, v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u euro. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Barca v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay Paulinho ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u H\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, anh \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i r\u1ed3i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Trung Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ec9 sau 11 th\u00e1ng phi\u00eau l\u01b0u t\u1ea1i La Liga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Barca v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Paulinho. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB Trung Qu\u1ed1c theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t 50 tri\u1ec7u euro, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 10 tri\u1ec7u euro so v\u1edbi l\u00fac Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paulinho tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u sau 11 th\u00e1ng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca\" title=\"Paulinho tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u sau 11 th\u00e1ng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/pau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Paulinho tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u sau 11 th\u00e1ng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paulinho Bezerra, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn mua \u0111\u1ee9t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo cho CLB Trung Qu\u1ed1c\u201d \u2013 trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u01b0a tin. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft \u01a1n v\u1edbi Paulinho v\u1ec1 cam k\u1ebft, s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ch\u00fac anh \u1ea5y may m\u1eafn, th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paulinho tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u sau 11 th\u00e1ng gia nh\u1eadp Barca, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ch\u01a1i t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 49 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ghi 9 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch (La Liga v\u00e0 c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 vua). \u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 55 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Brazil v\u00e0 ghi 13 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t Selecao \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/paulinho-thua-bi-con-dau-don-hon-tran-thua-duc-17-469-190586.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/paulinho-thua-bi-con-dau-don-hon-tran-thua-duc-17.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/paulinho-thua-bi-con-dau-don-hon-tran-thua-duc-17-469-190586.html\">Paulinho: Thua B\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn h\u01a1n tr\u1eadn thua \u0110\u1ee9c 1-7</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paulinho cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Brazil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua \u0110\u1ee9c 1-7 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/bong-da-va-cuoc-phieu-luu-kho-tin-cua-paulinho-389-190453.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/bong-da-va-cuoc-phieu-luu-kho-tin-cua-paulinho.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/bong-da-va-cuoc-phieu-luu-kho-tin-cua-paulinho-389-190453.html\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a Paulinho</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, m\u1ea5y ai \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec? V\u00e0 t\u00f4i, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u00e2m ni\u1ec7m r\u1eb1ng, Paulinho c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande, \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Paulinho \u1edf Barcelona c\u0169ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Uruguay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 Brazil c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua B\u1ec9 1-2. M\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Tite tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh \u2013 TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4070","checkdouble":"190739"},{"date":"07:06 09/07","title":"C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/11/1/co-mot-doi-bong-dang-lam-moi-cach-de-chieu-mo-sao-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, CLB H\u00e0 Lan Ajax n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Daley Blind \u2013 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><h2>Blind tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi M.U<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, nh\u01b0ng Daley Blind kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn. Qu\u00e1 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111ang t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Old Trafford.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau AS Roma \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y CLB c\u0169 Ajax l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. HLV c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 Lan, \u00f4ng Erik Ten Hag \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u00e1i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Daley Blind &ndash; c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2013-14 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ajax n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Daley Blind v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ajax n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Daley Blind v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/31/Ajax-no-luc-chieu-mo-Daley-Blind-vao-mua-he-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ajax n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Daley Blind v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m&rdquo; &ndash; Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ajax cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;Daley Blind \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia H\u00e0 Lan. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, trung v\u1ec7 l\u1eabn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Blind, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, ho\u1eb7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lisandro Magallan c\u1ee7a Boca Juniors. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi 1 trong 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Erik Ten Hag th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Ajax n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Daley Blind.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Jose Mourinho t\u1eebng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Blind trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Man United \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Marouane Fellaini, v\u00e0 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7/ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lindelof-tro-lai-mu-sau-that-bai-tai-world-cup-421-190729.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/lindelof-tro-lai-mu-sau-that-bai-tai-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lindelof-tro-lai-mu-sau-that-bai-tai-world-cup-421-190729.html\">Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tuy\u1ec3n Anh, \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga sau v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, trung v\u1ec7 Victor Lindelof tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U ngay...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-tranh-gianh-milinkovicsavic-voi-mu-172-190704.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/real-madrid-tranh-gianh-milinkovicsavic-voi-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-tranh-gianh-milinkovicsavic-voi-mu-172-190704.html\">Real Madrid tranh gi\u00e0nh Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi M.U</span><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Corriere dello Sport th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB Lazio \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y sang Real.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4069","checkdouble":"190731"},{"date":"22:31 08/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh ch\u00ea '\u0111\u00e0n em' C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/tuan-manh-3-1522935681.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 \u00fd ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u m\u00ecnh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League</span> tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Pleiku, khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-2, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh. Sau pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5m \u1ee9c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \"L\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111ang x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i nghe th\u1ea5y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi v\u0103ng t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi. C\u1eadu ta c\u00f2n d\u00f9ng m\u0169i gi\u00e0y ch\u1ecdc th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i khi t\u00f4i c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a t\u1ec9nh.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u1eadu ta c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec x\u00edch m\u00edch. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 cho c\u00e1c ch\u00fa l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HAGL x\u1eed l\u00fd vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng t\u00e2m h\u01a1n\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o ph\u00fat 80 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh b\u1ecb \u0111au sau m\u1ed9t pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean y t\u1ebf. V\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh c\u0169 \u1edf HAGL c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh c\u00e2u gi\u1edd khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111ang b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eabn t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ean.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4068","checkdouble":"190719"},{"date":"23:02 08/07","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi 'ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh' Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/14/hagl-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-chieu-mo-thu-mon-dt-lao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 8/7, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng to ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u00e2u gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac.\u00a0Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 'minh oan' cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng T\u1ea5n Anh cho bi\u1ebft: \"Ngay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ecfi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ea5y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u00f3 \u00fd tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, n\u00ean ch\u1ea1y l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i: '\u0110\u1ee9ng d\u1eady \u0111i, c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u m\u00e0 n\u1eb1m'. M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a th\u1ea5y v\u1eady li\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea9y Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn x\u1ea5n l\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n n\u00ean b\u1ecb th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u00ean k\u00ecm ch\u1ebf, tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng khi cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u00f3 l\u1eddi l\u1ebd x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m, khi\u00eau kh\u00edch khi\u1ebfn Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n \u1eefng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4067","checkdouble":"190720"},{"date":"00:11 09/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm song CLB HAGL cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh n\u00e0y.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>1. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 HAGL v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. L\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i khi \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 32 l\u1ea7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u00e0 hai CLB \u1edf nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 TP.HCM.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 ch\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Diem-nhan-tran-HAGL-2-4-Khanh-Hoa-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a G\u1ed7\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u00e1ch V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd 'G\u1ed7' l\u00ean nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00f4ng Tri\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay anh \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2 l\u00e0 A S\u00e2n. Sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00f4ng Tri\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 li\u1ec1n 2 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 39 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 44 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh Youssouf Toure.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, e r\u1eb1ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 CLB HAGL c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong t\u1ed1p 5 nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1 ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<h2>2. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u00e2n binh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, 'G\u1ed7' \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 an \u1ee7i khi hai t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n th\u1ee9 hai cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia Josip Zeba \u0111\u00e3 ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb pha treo b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. \u0110\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Josip ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Osmar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-2, song t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap HAGL gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh HAGL ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ngo\u1ea1i binh gi\u1ecfi trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n<h2>3. M\u00e0n t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t v\u00ec \u0103n \u0111\u1ee7 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00f4m nay (8/7) g\u1eb7p Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed3n cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An khi anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng do l\u1ed7i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u khi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 22, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat g\u1ed1c Ngh\u1ec7 An d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m nhanh nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ea9y ra. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 28, anh l\u1ea1i x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba v\u00e0 c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ai theo k\u00e8m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn chung, \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1ch g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh. Trong ph\u00fat n\u00f3ng n\u1ea3y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng v\u00ec h\u00f9ng h\u1ed5 g\u00e2y h\u1ea5n v\u1edbi Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh, khi cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u00e2u gi\u1edd. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang.</p>\r\n<h2>4. Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL, CLB Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu l\u00e9p v\u1ebf.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd phong t\u1ecfa g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 k\u00edn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh r\u1ed3i m\u01b0\u1ee3n s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Toure c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ed1c Ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng s\u1eafc l\u1ea1nh.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 bi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t set qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Tr\u00f9m T\u1ec9nh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1ed9i x\u00e0 ngang ph\u00fat 84 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o thay anh l\u00e0 Ho\u00e0i An s\u00fat b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t trong th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/36787800_1815071101918501_4864050149187387392_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>5. Th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n t\u1ea1i Pleiku gi\u00fap Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n \u0111ang c\u00f3 31 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai tr\u00ean BXH.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 19, xem ra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 Bi\u1ec3n l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c nh\u1ecf, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu gi\u1eef v\u1eefng phong \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai chung cu\u1ed9c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, HAGL c\u1ea7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n n\u1eefa sau tr\u1eadn thua v\u1eeba qua. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u1eafng tay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb SLNA v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean BXH. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 24 \u0111i\u1ec3m, k\u00e9m 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi SLNA v\u00e0 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi t\u1ed1p 3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng 8 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sinh t\u1eed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League sau vong 18\" title=\"BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/BXH-V-League-sau-vong-18.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4066","checkdouble":"190725"}]}